}}[[Classes]]: <u>BlasterSmoke</u><br>

The trail spawned behind a [[Classes:ArtiTomeOfPower|powered-up]] [[Classes:BlasterPowered|dragon claw]] [[Classes:BlasterFX1|shot]] as it travels. This is generated by the projectile's internal Tick() function rather than by an action function and is thus impossible to transcribe in DECORATE.

==== [[DECORATE]] definition ====
 ACTOR <u>BlasterSmoke</u>
 {
   +{{Flag|NOBLOCKMAP}}
   +{{Flag|NOGRAVITY}}
   +{{Flag|NOTELEPORT}}
   +{{Flag|CANNOTPUSH}}
   {{Property|RenderStyle}} Translucent
   {{Property|Alpha}} 0.4
   States
   {
   Spawn:
     FX18 HIJKL 4
     Stop
   }
 }
